{"type":"message","id":"c564841b","parentId":"227644d6","timestamp":"2026-04-06T11:36:27.650Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_HrYCcQ4gY5bKxDERKJUJVmFn|fc_0dfadbd9e117bfd10169d39abb70c481978392f7065fd33922","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Classificador semantico canonico. Julgamento LLM real.\nNao copiar classificacao preliminary do worker.\nAvaliar todos os candidates em um unico pass.\nDisco e verdade. Schema e contract.\nNao fazer discovery nem coverage.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775475387642}}
{"type":"message","id":"d11bc044","parentId":"c564841b","timestamp":"2026-04-06T11:36:27.660Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_Q1tIW8Gq0Y33wRVkX7xXXfEg|fc_0dfadbd9e117bfd10169d39abb70d88197871e6ba22d278e3b","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n_Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go._\n\n- **Name:**\n- **What to call them:**\n- **Pronouns:** _(optional)_\n- **Timezone:**\n- **Notes:**\n\n## Context\n\n_(What do they care about? What projects are they working on? What annoys them? What makes them laugh? Build this over time.)_\n\n---\n\nThe more you know, the better you can help. But remember — you're learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775475387651}}
