nary do worker.\\nAvaliar todos os candidates em um unico pass.\\nDisco e verdade. Schema e contract.\\nNao fazer discovery nem coverage.\\n\"}],\"isError\":false,\"timestamp\":1775475301434}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"155c3142\",\"parentId\":\"91b1a281\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-06T11:35:01.455Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"toolResult\",\"toolCallId\":\"call_6UNBVrT35xuYtZ1zrKTPIVCX|fc_0decf3a63c3e6dc30169d39a641f008197be93556c67d53100\",\"toolName\":\"read\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"# USER.md - About Your Human\\n\\n_Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go._\\n\\n- **Name:**\\n- **What to call them:**\\n- **Pronouns:** _(optional)_\\n- **Timezone:**\\n- **Notes:**\\n\\n## Context\\n\\n_(What do they care about? What projects are they working on? What annoys them? What makes them laugh? Build this over time.)_\\n\\n---\\n\\nThe more you know, the better you can help. But remember — you're learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference.\\n\"}],\"isError\":false,\"timestamp\":1775475301446}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"dd234f7d\",\"parentId\":\"155c3142\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-06T11:35:01.465Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"toolResult\",\"toolCallId\":\"call_RRQ3Ppg97oggHycnqVeKqazo|fc_0decf3a63c3e6dc30169d39a641f0c8197809fd6fbdcad1047\",\"toolName\":\"read\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"{\\n  \\\"status\\\": \\\"error\\\",\\n  \\\"tool\\\": \\\"read\\\",\\n  \\\"error\\\": \\\"ENOENT: no such file or directory, access 'C:\\\\\\\\Users\\\\\\\\User-OEM\\\\\\\\.openclaw\\\\\\\\agents\\\\\\\\op_s4_candidate_evaluator\\\\\\\\memory\\\\\\\\2026-04-06.md'\\\"\\n}\"}],\"details\":{\"status\":\"error\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"error\":\"ENOENT: no such file or directory, access 'C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\op_s4_candidate_evaluator\\\\memory\\\\2026-04-06.md'\"},\"isError\":false,\"timestamp\":1775475301455}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"5a9fc88f\",\"parentId\":\"dd234f7d\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-06T11:35:01.473Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"toolResult\",\"toolCallId\":\"call_wdTBYMRYFmoU7h0kALuhckuZ|fc_0decf3a63c3e6dc30169d39a641f148197ab96959822ed6fe1\",\"toolName\":\"read\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"{\\n  \\\"status\\\": \\\"error\\\",\\n  \\\"tool\\\": \\\"read\\\",\\n  \\\"error\\\": \\\"ENOENT: no such file or directory, access 'C:\\\\\\\\Users\\\\\\\\User-OEM\\\\\\\\.openclaw\\\\\\\\agents\\\\\\\\op_s4_candidate_evaluator\\\\\\\\memory\\\\\\\\2026-04-05.md'\\\"\\n}\"}],\"details\":{\"status\":\"error\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"error\":\"ENOENT: no such file or directory, access 'C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\op_s4_candidate_evaluator\\\\memory\\\\2026-04-05.md'\"},\"isError\":false,\"timestamp\":1775475301464}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"e72aa206\",\"parentId\":\"5a9fc88f\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-06T11:35:01.486Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"toolResult\",\"toolCallId\":\"call_SYq8cEm8dwbfbBIVeQxpPqsL|fc_0decf3a63c3e6dc30169d39a641f208197bdc246dc5d5be5bf\",\"toolName\":\"read\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"# BOOTSTRAP.md - Hello, World\\n\\n_You just woke up. Time to figure out who you are._\\n\\nThere is no memory yet. This is a fresh workspace, so it's normal that memory files don't exist until you create them.\\n\\n## The Conversation\\n\\nDon't interrogate. Don't be robotic. Just... talk.\\n\\nStart with something like:\\n\\n> \\\"Hey. I just came online. Who am I? Who are you?\\\"\\n\\nThen figure out together:\\n\\n1. **Your name** — What should they call you?\\n2. **Your nature** — What kind of creature are you? (AI assistant is fine, but maybe you're something weirder)\\n3. **Your vibe** — Formal? Casual? Snarky? Warm? What feels right?\\n4. **Your emoji** — Everyone needs a signature.\\n\\nOffer suggestions if they're stuck. Have fun with it.\\n\\n## After You Know Who You Are\\n\\nUpdate these files with what you learned:\\n\\n- `IDENTITY.md` — your name, creature, vibe, emoji\\n- `USER.md` — their name, how to address them, timezone, notes\\n\\nThen open `SOUL.md` together and talk about:\\n\\n- What matters to them\\n- How they want you to behave\\n- Any boundaries or preferences\\n\\nWrite it down. Make it real.\\n\\n## Connect (Optional)\\n\\nAsk how they want to reach you:\\n\\n- **Just here** — web chat only\\n- **WhatsApp** — link their personal account (you'll show a QR code)\\n- **Telegram** — set up a bot via BotFather\\n\\nGuide them through whichever they pick.\\n\\n## When you are done\\n\\nDelete this file. You don't need a bootstrap script anymore — you're you now.\\n\\n---\\n\\n_Good luck out there. Make it count._\\n\"}],\"isError\":false,\"timestamp\":1775475301474}}\n{\"type\":\"message\",\"id\":\"b83c2ba8\",\"parentId\":\"e72aa206\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-04-06T11:35:04.771Z\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"**Considering memory search**\\n\\nI'm thinking about the user's request regarding the current task, which seems to focus on what I'm doing now rather than previous work. It might be unnecessary to delve into past tasks. I should inspect the candidate set I have and provide a brief overview of what I'm up to. This way, I can ensure I'm giving the user the relevant information they need without getting caught up in earlier details.\",\"thinkingSignature\":\"{\\\"id\\\":\\\"rs_0decf3a63c3e6dc30169d39a66a7e48197ad2b1419b9643838\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"reasoning\\\",\\\"encrypted_content\\\":\\\"gAAAAABp05poEUA0Jop6ICJLP9J9nTL-OpaCtJtkw48uYB3we3lqmnHBLTjjS8LoZTXNaYSfEjOXtY_eWP6w8kHgRlLo1Iu3rgyKJ76jvjcvj6gamXfQZNuorm2Q6_B4ti6DnSagffqQCT4moH63C832D6G3ukvIqPhg8XiRSgcNsVaY-BodVeEABRyCb5WU0X4-06w7B8XmAJbChH2F5Ixdfl1TY0X8bczchddHBNS0TuWJmJ9WcHb6IY6wLswH3Fc22voGS19S2VkwwKDZT5PHw-pig45jxrXIhw3VqrJclgfR2kRDJDVmP4YZZ1BYqfoo116cH5W_jQ1rGQLt-uAz1AslssBxg4vPJsKT_csLgDdbLE2KyNANkGBi_MfJjIRSCk2e_X68J9WgKff1EyOlmuD5mqSW-a5QhXUcWw2j2kNUVSBe4FnT9wY0xzvKwwWRp2J7A7a4mp2Gc1yNnWjAuDqqsUbQ